---
title: Double Cheese Harissa Chicken Pasta Bake with Pepper and Spinach
description: Pasta bakes are a crowd-pleasing dish, typically pairing tomatoey sauces with gooey melted cheese. Here, we're using twice the cheese with mozzarella and Cheddar, paired with a punchy harissa sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R42_W21_UK_V11701-19_Main__4low-6682e4c6.jpg
